name: Depleted (BranchingLantern)
description:
In DEPLETED, time is money and we all need money to live right?

Be careful to choose your tasks wisely or suffer the consequences!

Honestly, maybe we're not all cutout for this...

Created for a mock game jam with the theme of the same name, DEPLETED takes you through the day to day life of a burnt out developer.

It was created in under 48 hours.
